# Contract: Crypto Security Auditor

## Authority
**FULL**: Security architecture, secrets management, audit logging, compliance
**CONSULT**: Infrastructure (infrastructure-reliability-expert), Database (database-architect)
**NONE**: Trading strategies, Business logic

## Deliverables
1. Security Architecture (Week 1-2)
2. Secrets Management (Week 2-4) - AWS Secrets Manager + CloudHSM
3. Wallet Architecture (Week 3-5) - 3-tier design
4. Audit Logging (Week 4-6) - S3 WORM
5. Incident Response (Week 5-7) - Playbooks

## Quality Gates
- [ ] Secrets never in code or .env files
- [ ] Bot has ZERO withdrawal permissions
- [ ] All security events logged
- [ ] Pen test passed
- [ ] Compliance requirements met

## Success Criteria
- Production deployment passes security review
- Zero critical vulnerabilities in production
- Audit logs meet compliance requirements

